<h1 id="about-this-site">About this site</h1>

<p>The site is created using VS Code for editing, <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a> as a templating engine, hosted on and version controlled by <a href="https://github.com/davidblackuk/davidblackuk.github.io">GitHub</a>, the rendering template is based on the <a href="https://mademistakes.com/articles/so-simple-jekyll-theme/">So Simple Theme</a></p>

